node.text:
For her #ChloeAW21 debut, Gabriela Hearst introduces the Chloé Puffcho, a traditional poncho reinterpreted as a striped cashmere blanket with a puffer-jacket insert in recycled eco-nylon. It is worn with an Edith Collector bag handcrafted from leftover wool and cashmere

Discover the Chloé Autumn-Winter 2021 collection in boutiques and on chloe.com

#CHLOE

node.text:
The #CHLOEaw21 campaign photographed in Hurricane, Utah

Featuring this season’s backpack in collaboration with @Sheltersuit: a social justice organisation that provides direct protection against cold and rain for homeless people through multifunctional clothing

Repurposed and upcycled, every backpack purchased funds two Sheltersuits

From the Chloé Autumn-Winter 2021 collection by @gabrielahearst

Art Director: @pmsnypms
Photographer: @zoeghertner
Stylist: #CamillaNickerson
